Image Build
-----------
1) Install oz
    apt-get install oz # Ubuntu
    yum install oz # RedHat/CentOS
2) Modify template file in templates/ and change the <rootpw> section in the .tdl for the distribution you want to modify
3) build the image
    ./build.sh f16 # will built a fedora 16 image
4) Copy the distro.img.gz file to your nova infra node and add it to glance
    zcat distro.img.gz | keyglance <admin user> <admin password> add name="<IMAGE NAME>" container_format=bare disk_format=raw is_Public="True"
5) Launch an instance and enjoy

